ces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da16bcda0e6dc37d634eb06a43cc5755850c442","tid":81352,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係瀨屎既諧音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用黎形容食物既味道似屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但由於太唔文雅 比人改下改下就變左做拉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b03051d8ac1d344bcd8f31e5f413740f058718fe","tid":81352,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"NICE!"}]}